snippet.title: Games of Glory - PSX 2016 Gameplay Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Fight alongside friends to earn fame and fortune in the intergalactic arenas of the Synarchy! Games of Glory is a brand new, free-to-play, top-down team shooter, coming to PlayStation 4 in early 2017. 

Learn more at http://games-of-glory.com
